name: Bill Clinton
abstract: William Jefferson "Bill" Clinton is an American politician who served as the 42nd President of the United States from 1993 to 2001. Inaugurated at age 46, he was the third-youngest president.
related_searches: Hillary Rodham Clinton is Bill Clinton's spouse.
